This script:

Installs dependencies

Clones tools (RED HAWK, fsociety)

Creates a global WEBSITE command



---

🚀 Usage

After installation, simply type:

WEBSITE

You'll get a full interactive menu with tools like:

WHOIS via RDAP

RED HAWK (SQLi scanner, CMS detection)

fsociety hacking toolkit

Nmap port scan

Subdomain scanner

CMS fingerprinting



---

🧰 Features

#	Tool Name	Description

1	RED HAWK	All-in-one PHP-based website scanner
2	fsociety	Pen-testing toolkit from Mr. Robot series
3	RDAP WHOIS	Clean domain ownership info
4	Subdomain Scanner	Uses Hackertarget API
5	CMS Detector	Detects WordPress, Joomla, etc
6	Nmap	Basic TCP port scanning



---

⚙️ Requirements

✅ Termux on Android

✅ Internet access

❌ No root needed



---

